### POST /enquiry — Create a new enquiry
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Sarah Mitchell",
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "message": "Hi, I'd like to book an appointment for next week."
}

###

### POST /enquiry — Pricing question
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Raj Patel",
  "channel": "email",
  "message": "Can you tell me the price for your premium package?"
}

###

### POST /enquiry — No SOP match (will escalate)
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "James Liu",
  "channel": "call",
  "message": "Just calling to say hi, nothing specific."
}

###

### POST /enquiry/{id}/follow-up — Schedule a follow-up (replace {id} with real enquiry id)
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry/enq_REPLACE_ME/follow-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 60,
  "message_template": "Hi {name}, just following up on your appointment request!"
}

###

### POST /enquiry/{id}/escalate — Manually escalate an enquiry
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry/enq_REPLACE_ME/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer is requesting to speak with a senior manager."
}

###

### GET /enquiry/{id}/history — Fetch enquiry + timeline
GET http://localhost:8000/enquiry/enq_REPLACE_ME/history

###

### GET /health — Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
